00:37:44,796 --> 00:37:46,640
I've always thought
of archeology

717
00:37:46,664 --> 00:37:49,643
as the most democratic
form of history

718
00:37:49,667 --> 00:37:52,947
because it isn't
just what the people

719
00:37:52,971 --> 00:37:54,782
who knew how to write say,

720
00:37:54,806 --> 00:38:00,421
and it isn't just what
a more elite class

721
00:38:00,445 --> 00:38:03,791
of people left behind.

722
00:38:03,815 --> 00:38:06,393
- After working at the site
for several years,

723
00:38:06,417 --> 00:38:10,464
Deagan and her team found a well
that was typical of European

724
00:38:10,488 --> 00:38:13,400
rather than Native American
construction.

725
00:38:13,424 --> 00:38:16,203
Its contents led them to believe

726
00:38:16,227 --> 00:38:19,440
that this was the site
of the first settlement

