00:38:23,902 --> 00:38:26,413
We said, "No. This couldn't have
been here all this time,"

730
00:38:26,437 --> 00:38:29,683
and here we've been
working for over 30 years

731
00:38:29,707 --> 00:38:31,585
on and off at this site.

732
00:38:31,609 --> 00:38:34,321
- They found the site while
digging at the Fountain of Youth

733
00:38:34,345 --> 00:38:38,559
Archaeological Park
just north of downtown.

734
00:38:38,583 --> 00:38:44,598
- It was enough mass to convince
us even after 30 years

735
00:38:44,622 --> 00:38:47,334
that it really was
the Menéndez settlement.

736
00:38:47,358 --> 00:38:49,470
- They found hundreds
of artifacts,

